.container

  - if user_signed_in?
    #swf-container
      / Container to load SWFObject with the infiltration flash project (done on home.js.coffee)

  - else
    %p
      = link_to 'Sign in', new_user_session_path
      or
      = link_to 'create a new account', new_user_registration_path
      to
      %b play ranked
      and
      %b create new maps.
    %p
      Or click on a map in the
      = link_to 'Maps Ranking', maps_ladder_path
      to play anonymously on
      %b free-play mode.
